FROM (
    SELECT u."Id", u."FirstName", u."LastName", u."UserName", (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f
        WHERE u."Id" = f."FollowingId") AS c, (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f0
        WHERE u."Id" = f0."FollowerId") AS c0
    FROM "Users" AS u
    WHERE NOT (u."IsDeleted") AND u."Id" = @__userId_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS u0
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f3."Id", f3."Id0", f3."FollowingId"
    FROM (
        SELECT f1."FollowerId" AS "Id", f1."Id" AS "Id0", f1."FollowingId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f1."FollowingId" ORDER BY f1."Id" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Follows" AS f1

SELECT u0."Id", u0."FirstName", u0."LastName", u0."UserName", u0.c, u0.c0, f4."Id", f4."Id0", f6."Id", f6."Id0"
FROM (
    SELECT u."Id", u."FirstName", u."LastName", u."UserName", (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f
        WHERE u."Id" = f."FollowingId") AS c, (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f0
        WHERE u."Id" = f0."FollowerId") AS c0
    FROM "Users" AS u
    WHERE NOT (u."IsDeleted") AND u."UserName" = @__userName_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS u0
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f3."Id", f3."Id0", f3."FollowingId"
    FROM (
        SELECT f1."FollowerId" AS "Id", f1."Id" AS "Id0", f1."FollowingId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f1."FollowingId" ORDER BY f1."Id" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Follows" AS f1
    ) AS f3
    WHERE f3.row <= 10
) AS f4 ON u0."Id" = f4."FollowingId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f5."Id", f5."Id0", f5."FollowerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT f2."FollowingId" AS "Id", f2."Id" AS "Id0", f2."FollowerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f2."FollowerId" ORDER BY f2."Id" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Follows" AS f2
    ) AS f5
    WHERE f5.row <= 10
) AS f6 ON u0."Id" = f6."FollowerId"
ORDER BY u0."Id", f4."FollowingId", f4."Id0" DESC, f6."FollowerId", f6."Id0" DESC

FROM (
    SELECT u."Id", u."FirstName", u."LastName", u."UserName", (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f
        WHERE u."Id" = f."FollowingId") AS c, (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f0
        WHERE u."Id" = f0."FollowerId") AS c0
    FROM "Users" AS u
    WHERE NOT (u."IsDeleted") AND u."UserName" = @__userName_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS u0
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f3."Id", f3."Id0", f3."FollowingId"
    FROM (
        SELECT f1."FollowerId" AS "Id", f1."Id" AS "Id0", f1."FollowingId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f1."FollowingId" ORDER BY f1."Id" DESC) AS row

) AS f6 ON u0."Id" = f6."FollowerId"

        SELECT count(*)::int

        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f0
        WHERE u."Id" = f0."FollowerId") AS c0

    WHERE NOT (u."IsDeleted") AND u."UserName" = @__userName_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS u0

FROM (
    SELECT u."Id", u."FirstName", u."LastName", u."UserName", (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f
        WHERE u."Id" = f."FollowingId") AS c, (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f0
        WHERE u."Id" = f0."FollowerId") AS c0
    FROM "Users" AS u
    WHERE NOT (u."IsDeleted") AND u."UserName" = @__userName_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS u0
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f3."Id", f3."Id0", f3."FollowingId"
    FROM (
        SELECT f1."FollowerId" AS "Id", f1."Id" AS "Id0", f1."FollowingId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f1."FollowingId" ORDER BY f1."Id" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Follows" AS f1
    ) AS f3
    WHERE f3.row <= 10
) AS f4 ON u0."Id" = f4."FollowingId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f5."Id", f5."Id0", f5."FollowerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT f2."FollowingId" AS "Id", f2."Id" AS "Id0", f2."FollowerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f2."FollowerId" ORDER BY f2."Id" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Follows" AS f2
    ) AS f5
    WHERE f5.row <= 10
) AS f6 ON u0."Id" = f6."FollowerId"
ORDER BY u0."Id", f4."FollowingId", f4."Id0" DESC, f6."FollowerId", f6."Id0" DESC

    WHERE NOT (u."IsDeleted") AND u."Id" = @__userId_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS u0

        FROM "Follows" AS f1
    ) AS f3
    WHERE f3.row <= 10
) AS f4 ON u0."Id" = f4."FollowingId"

    SELECT f5."Id", f5."Id0", f5."FollowerId"

FROM (
    SELECT u."Id", u."FirstName", u."LastName", u."UserName", (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f
        WHERE u."Id" = f."FollowingId") AS c, (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f0
        WHERE u."Id" = f0."FollowerId") AS c0
    FROM "Users" AS u
    WHERE NOT (u."IsDeleted") AND u."UserName" = @__userName_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS u0
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f3."Id", f3."Id0", f3."FollowingId"
    FROM (
        SELECT f1."FollowerId" AS "Id", f1."Id" AS "Id0", f1."FollowingId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f1."FollowingId" ORDER BY f1."Id" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Follows" AS f1
    ) AS f3
    WHERE f3.row <= 10
) AS f4 ON u0."Id" = f4."FollowingId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f5."Id", f5."Id0", f5."FollowerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT f2."FollowingId" AS "Id", f2."Id" AS "Id0", f2."FollowerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f2."FollowerId" ORDER BY f2."Id" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Follows" AS f2
    ) AS f5
    WHERE f5.row <= 10
) AS f6 ON u0."Id" = f6."FollowerId"
ORDER BY u0."Id", f4."FollowingId", f4."Id0" DESC, f6."FollowerId", f6."Id0" DESC

SELECT u0."Id", u0."FirstName", u0."LastName", u0."UserName", u0.c, u0.c0, f4."Id", f4."Id0", f6."Id", f6."Id0"
FROM (
    SELECT u."Id", u."FirstName", u."LastName", u."UserName", (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f
        WHERE u."Id" = f."FollowingId") AS c, (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f0
        WHERE u."Id" = f0."FollowerId") AS c0
    FROM "Users" AS u
    WHERE NOT (u."IsDeleted") AND u."UserName" = @__userName_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS u0
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f3."Id", f3."Id0", f3."FollowingId"
    FROM (
        SELECT f1."FollowerId" AS "Id", f1."Id" AS "Id0", f1."FollowingId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f1."FollowingId" ORDER BY f1."Id" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Follows" AS f1
    ) AS f3
    WHERE f3.row <= 10
) AS f4 ON u0."Id" = f4."FollowingId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f5."Id", f5."Id0", f5."FollowerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT f2."FollowingId" AS "Id", f2."Id" AS "Id0", f2."FollowerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f2."FollowerId" ORDER BY f2."Id" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Follows" AS f2
    ) AS f5
    WHERE f5.row <= 10
) AS f6 ON u0."Id" = f6."FollowerId"
ORDER BY u0."Id", f4."FollowingId", f4."Id0" DESC, f6."FollowerId", f6."Id0" DESC

FROM (
    SELECT u."Id", u."FirstName", u."LastName", u."UserName", (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f
        WHERE u."Id" = f."FollowingId") AS c, (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f0
        WHERE u."Id" = f0."FollowerId") AS c0
    FROM "Users" AS u
    WHERE NOT (u."IsDeleted") AND u."UserName" = @__userName_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS u0
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f3."Id", f3."Id0", f3."FollowingId"

        SELECT f1."FollowerId" AS "Id", f1."Id" AS "Id0", f1."FollowingId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f1."FollowingId" ORDER BY f1."Id" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Follows" AS f1
    ) AS f3
    WHERE f3.row <= 10
) AS f4 ON u0."Id" = f4."FollowingId"

    SELECT f5."Id", f5."Id0", f5."FollowerId"

        SELECT f2."FollowingId" AS "Id", f2."Id" AS "Id0", f2."FollowerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f2."FollowerId" ORDER BY f2."Id" DESC) AS row

    ) AS f5
    WHERE f5.row <= 10
) AS f6 ON u0."Id" = f6."FollowerId"

SELECT u0."Id", u0."FirstName", u0."LastName", u0."UserName", u0.c, u0.c0, f4."Id", f4."Id0", f6."Id", f6."Id0"
FROM (
    SELECT u."Id", u."FirstName", u."LastName", u."UserName", (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f
        WHERE u."Id" = f."FollowingId") AS c, (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f0
        WHERE u."Id" = f0."FollowerId") AS c0
    FROM "Users" AS u
    WHERE NOT (u."IsDeleted") AND u."UserName" = @__userName_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS u0
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f3."Id", f3."Id0", f3."FollowingId"
    FROM (
        SELECT f1."FollowerId" AS "Id", f1."Id" AS "Id0", f1."FollowingId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f1."FollowingId" ORDER BY f1."Id" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Follows" AS f1
    ) AS f3
    WHERE f3.row <= 10
) AS f4 ON u0."Id" = f4."FollowingId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f5."Id", f5."Id0", f5."FollowerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT f2."FollowingId" AS "Id", f2."Id" AS "Id0", f2."FollowerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f2."FollowerId" ORDER BY f2."Id" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Follows" AS f2
    ) AS f5
    WHERE f5.row <= 10
) AS f6 ON u0."Id" = f6."FollowerId"
ORDER BY u0."Id", f4."FollowingId", f4."Id0" DESC, f6."FollowerId", f6."Id0" DESC

FROM (
    SELECT u."Id", u."FirstName", u."LastName", u."UserName", (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f
        WHERE u."Id" = f."FollowingId") AS c, (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f0
        WHERE u."Id" = f0."FollowerId") AS c0
    FROM "Users" AS u
    WHERE NOT (u."IsDeleted") AND u."UserName" = @__userName_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS u0
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f3."Id", f3."Id0", f3."FollowingId"
    FROM (
        SELECT f1."FollowerId" AS "Id", f1."Id" AS "Id0", f1."FollowingId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f1."FollowingId" ORDER BY f1."Id" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Follows" AS f1
    ) AS f3
    WHERE f3.row <= 10
) AS f4 ON u0."Id" = f4."FollowingId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f5."Id", f5."Id0", f5."FollowerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT f2."FollowingId" AS "Id", f2."Id" AS "Id0", f2."FollowerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f2."FollowerId" ORDER BY f2."Id" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Follows" AS f2
    ) AS f5
    WHERE f5.row <= 10
) AS f6 ON u0."Id" = f6."FollowerId"

SELECT p0."Id", p0."Body", p0."CreatedAt", p0."DeletedAt", p0."IsDeleted", p0."Status", p0."UpdatedAt", p0."UserId", u."Id", u."CreatedAt", u."DeletedAt", u."Email", u."FirstName", u."IsDeleted", u."LastName", u."PasswordHash", u."PasswordSalt", u."RoleId", u."UpdatedAt", u."UserName", l."Id", l."CreatedAt", l."DeletedAt", l."IsDeleted", l."PostId", l."UpdatedAt", l."UserId", s."Id", s."Body", s."CreatedAt", s."DeletedAt", s."IsDeleted", s."PostId", s."UpdatedAt", s."UserId", s."CommentId", s."Discriminator", p1."Id", p1."CreatedAt", p1."DeletedAt", p1."File", p1."IsDeleted", p1."PostId", p1."UpdatedAt", p2."Id", p2."CreatedAt", p2."DeletedAt", p2."File", p2."IsDeleted", p2."PostId", p2."UpdatedAt"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Body", p."CreatedAt", p."DeletedAt", p."IsDeleted", p."Status", p."UpdatedAt", p."UserId"
    FROM "Posts" AS p
    WHERE NOT (p."IsDeleted") AND p."UserId" IN (
        SELECT f."FollowingId"
        FROM "Follows" AS f
        WHERE NOT (f."IsDeleted") AND f."FollowerId" = @__userId_0
    )
    ORDER BY p."CreatedAt" DESC, p."Id" DESC
    LIMIT @__p_2 OFFSET @__p_1
) AS p0
INNER JOIN "Users" AS u ON p0."UserId" = u."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Likes" AS l ON p0."Id" = l."PostId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT c."Id", c."Body", c."CreatedAt", c."DeletedAt", c."IsDeleted", c."PostId", c."UpdatedAt", c."UserId", r."CommentId", CASE
        WHEN r."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN 'CommentResponse'
    END AS "Discriminator"
    FROM "Comments" AS c
    LEFT JOIN "Responses" AS r ON c."Id" = r."Id"
) AS s ON p0."Id" = s."PostId"
LEFT JOIN "PostBrutals" AS p1 ON p0."Id" = p1."PostId"
LEFT JOIN "PostImages" AS p2 ON p0."Id" = p2."PostId"

FROM (
    SELECT u."Id", u."FirstName", u."LastName", u."UserName", (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f
        WHERE u."Id" = f."FollowingId") AS c, (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f0
        WHERE u."Id" = f0."FollowerId") AS c0
    FROM "Users" AS u
    WHERE NOT (u."IsDeleted") AND u."UserName" = @__userName_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS u0
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f3."Id", f3."Id0", f3."FollowingId"
    FROM (
        SELECT f1."FollowerId" AS "Id", f1."Id" AS "Id0", f1."FollowingId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f1."FollowingId" ORDER BY f1."Id" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Follows" AS f1
    ) AS f3
    WHERE f3.row <= 10
) AS f4 ON u0."Id" = f4."FollowingId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f5."Id", f5."Id0", f5."FollowerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT f2."FollowingId" AS "Id", f2."Id" AS "Id0", f2."FollowerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f2."FollowerId" ORDER BY f2."Id" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Follows" AS f2
    ) AS f5
    WHERE f5.row <= 10
) AS f6 ON u0."Id" = f6."FollowerId"
ORDER BY u0."Id", f4."FollowingId", f4."Id0" DESC, f6."FollowerId", f6."Id0" DESC

        SELECT f."FollowingId"
        FROM "Follows" AS f
        WHERE NOT (f."IsDeleted") AND f."FollowerId" = @__userId_0
    )
    ORDER BY p."CreatedAt" DESC, p."Id" DESC
    LIMIT @__p_2 OFFSET @__p_1
) AS p0
INNER JOIN "Users" AS u ON p0."UserId" = u."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Likes" AS l ON p0."Id" = l."PostId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT c."Id", c."Body", c."CreatedAt", c."DeletedAt", c."IsDeleted", c."PostId", c."UpdatedAt", c."UserId", r."CommentId", CASE

    END AS "Discriminator"

    LEFT JOIN "Responses" AS r ON c."Id" = r."Id"
) AS s ON p0."Id" = s."PostId"

FROM (
    SELECT u."Id", u."FirstName", u."LastName", u."UserName", (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f
        WHERE u."Id" = f."FollowingId") AS c, (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f0
        WHERE u."Id" = f0."FollowerId") AS c0
    FROM "Users" AS u
    WHERE NOT (u."IsDeleted") AND u."UserName" = @__userName_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS u0
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f3."Id", f3."Id0", f3."FollowingId"
    FROM (
        SELECT f1."FollowerId" AS "Id", f1."Id" AS "Id0", f1."FollowingId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f1."FollowingId" ORDER BY f1."Id" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Follows" AS f1
    ) AS f3
    WHERE f3.row <= 10
) AS f4 ON u0."Id" = f4."FollowingId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f5."Id", f5."Id0", f5."FollowerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT f2."FollowingId" AS "Id", f2."Id" AS "Id0", f2."FollowerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f2."FollowerId" ORDER BY f2."Id" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Follows" AS f2
    ) AS f5
    WHERE f5.row <= 10
) AS f6 ON u0."Id" = f6."FollowerId"
ORDER BY u0."Id", f4."FollowingId", f4."Id0" DESC, f6."FollowerId", f6."Id0" DESC

FROM (
    SELECT u."Id", u."FirstName", u."LastName", u."UserName", (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f
        WHERE u."Id" = f."FollowingId") AS c, (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f0
        WHERE u."Id" = f0."FollowerId") AS c0
    FROM "Users" AS u
    WHERE NOT (u."IsDeleted") AND u."UserName" = @__userName_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS u0
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f3."Id", f3."Id0", f3."FollowingId"
    FROM (
        SELECT f1."FollowerId" AS "Id", f1."Id" AS "Id0", f1."FollowingId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f1."FollowingId" ORDER BY f1."Id" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Follows" AS f1
    ) AS f3
    WHERE f3.row <= 10
) AS f4 ON u0."Id" = f4."FollowingId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f5."Id", f5."Id0", f5."FollowerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT f2."FollowingId" AS "Id", f2."Id" AS "Id0", f2."FollowerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f2."FollowerId" ORDER BY f2."Id" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Follows" AS f2
    ) AS f5
    WHERE f5.row <= 10
) AS f6 ON u0."Id" = f6."FollowerId"
ORDER BY u0."Id", f4."FollowingId", f4."Id0" DESC, f6."FollowerId", f6."Id0" DESC

FROM (
    SELECT u."Id", u."FirstName", u."LastName", u."UserName", (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f
        WHERE u."Id" = f."FollowingId") AS c, (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f0
        WHERE u."Id" = f0."FollowerId") AS c0
    FROM "Users" AS u
    WHERE NOT (u."IsDeleted") AND u."UserName" = @__userName_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS u0
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f3."Id", f3."Id0", f3."FollowingId"
    FROM (
        SELECT f1."FollowerId" AS "Id", f1."Id" AS "Id0", f1."FollowingId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f1."FollowingId" ORDER BY f1."Id" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Follows" AS f1
    ) AS f3
    WHERE f3.row <= 10
) AS f4 ON u0."Id" = f4."FollowingId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f5."Id", f5."Id0", f5."FollowerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT f2."FollowingId" AS "Id", f2."Id" AS "Id0", f2."FollowerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f2."FollowerId" ORDER BY f2."Id" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Follows" AS f2
    ) AS f5
    WHERE f5.row <= 10
) AS f6 ON u0."Id" = f6."FollowerId"

FROM (
    SELECT u."Id", u."FirstName", u."LastName", u."UserName", (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f
        WHERE u."Id" = f."FollowingId") AS c, (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f0
        WHERE u."Id" = f0."FollowerId") AS c0
    FROM "Users" AS u
    WHERE NOT (u."IsDeleted") AND u."UserName" = @__userName_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS u0
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f3."Id", f3."Id0", f3."FollowingId"
    FROM (
        SELECT f1."FollowerId" AS "Id", f1."Id" AS "Id0", f1."FollowingId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f1."FollowingId" ORDER BY f1."Id" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Follows" AS f1
    ) AS f3
    WHERE f3.row <= 10
) AS f4 ON u0."Id" = f4."FollowingId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f5."Id", f5."Id0", f5."FollowerId"

    ) AS f5
    WHERE f5.row <= 10
) AS f6 ON u0."Id" = f6."FollowerId"

SELECT u0."Id", u0."FirstName", u0."LastName", u0."UserName", u0.c, u0.c0, f4."Id", f4."Id0", f6."Id", f6."Id0"
FROM (
    SELECT u."Id", u."FirstName", u."LastName", u."UserName", (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f
        WHERE u."Id" = f."FollowingId") AS c, (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f0
        WHERE u."Id" = f0."FollowerId") AS c0
    FROM "Users" AS u
    WHERE NOT (u."IsDeleted") AND u."UserName" = @__userName_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS u0
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f3."Id", f3."Id0", f3."FollowingId"
    FROM (
        SELECT f1."FollowerId" AS "Id", f1."Id" AS "Id0", f1."FollowingId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f1."FollowingId" ORDER BY f1."Id" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Follows" AS f1
    ) AS f3
    WHERE f3.row <= 10
) AS f4 ON u0."Id" = f4."FollowingId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f5."Id", f5."Id0", f5."FollowerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT f2."FollowingId" AS "Id", f2."Id" AS "Id0", f2."FollowerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f2."FollowerId" ORDER BY f2."Id" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Follows" AS f2
    ) AS f5
    WHERE f5.row <= 10
) AS f6 ON u0."Id" = f6."FollowerId"
ORDER BY u0."Id", f4."FollowingId", f4."Id0" DESC, f6."FollowerId", f6."Id0" DESC

FROM (
    SELECT u."Id", u."FirstName", u."LastName", u."UserName", (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f
        WHERE u."Id" = f."FollowingId") AS c, (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f0
        WHERE u."Id" = f0."FollowerId") AS c0
    FROM "Users" AS u
    WHERE NOT (u."IsDeleted") AND u."Id" = @__userId_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS u0
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f3."Id", f3."Id0", f3."FollowingId"
    FROM (
        SELECT f1."FollowerId" AS "Id", f1."Id" AS "Id0", f1."FollowingId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f1."FollowingId" ORDER BY f1."Id" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Follows" AS f1
    ) AS f3
    WHERE f3.row <= 10
) AS f4 ON u0."Id" = f4."FollowingId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f5."Id", f5."Id0", f5."FollowerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT f2."FollowingId" AS "Id", f2."Id" AS "Id0", f2."FollowerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f2."FollowerId" ORDER BY f2."Id" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Follows" AS f2
    ) AS f5
    WHERE f5.row <= 10
) AS f6 ON u0."Id" = f6."FollowerId"

FROM (
    SELECT u."Id", u."FirstName", u."LastName", u."UserName", (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f
        WHERE u."Id" = f."FollowingId") AS c, (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f0
        WHERE u."Id" = f0."FollowerId") AS c0
    FROM "Users" AS u
    WHERE NOT (u."IsDeleted") AND u."UserName" = @__userName_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS u0
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f3."Id", f3."Id0", f3."FollowingId"
    FROM (
        SELECT f1."FollowerId" AS "Id", f1."Id" AS "Id0", f1."FollowingId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f1."FollowingId" ORDER BY f1."Id" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Follows" AS f1
    ) AS f3
    WHERE f3.row <= 10
) AS f4 ON u0."Id" = f4."FollowingId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f5."Id", f5."Id0", f5."FollowerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT f2."FollowingId" AS "Id", f2."Id" AS "Id0", f2."FollowerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f2."FollowerId" ORDER BY f2."Id" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Follows" AS f2
    ) AS f5
    WHERE f5.row <= 10
) AS f6 ON u0."Id" = f6."FollowerId"

SELECT u0."Id", u0."FirstName", u0."LastName", u0."UserName", u0.c, u0.c0, f4."Id", f4."Id0", f6."Id", f6."Id0"
FROM (
    SELECT u."Id", u."FirstName", u."LastName", u."UserName", (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f
        WHERE u."Id" = f."FollowingId") AS c, (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f0
        WHERE u."Id" = f0."FollowerId") AS c0
    FROM "Users" AS u
    WHERE NOT (u."IsDeleted") AND u."Id" = @__userId_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS u0
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f3."Id", f3."Id0", f3."FollowingId"
    FROM (
        SELECT f1."FollowerId" AS "Id", f1."Id" AS "Id0", f1."FollowingId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f1."FollowingId" ORDER BY f1."Id" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Follows" AS f1
    ) AS f3
    WHERE f3.row <= 10
) AS f4 ON u0."Id" = f4."FollowingId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f5."Id", f5."Id0", f5."FollowerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT f2."FollowingId" AS "Id", f2."Id" AS "Id0", f2."FollowerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f2."FollowerId" ORDER BY f2."Id" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Follows" AS f2
    ) AS f5
    WHERE f5.row <= 10
) AS f6 ON u0."Id" = f6."FollowerId"
ORDER BY u0."Id", f4."FollowingId", f4."Id0" DESC, f6."FollowerId", f6."Id0" DESC

    )
    ORDER BY p."CreatedAt" DESC, p."Id" DESC

2025-12-23 16:29:27.306 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (66ms) [Parameters=[@__userId_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT u0."Id", u0."FirstName", u0."LastName", u0."UserName", u0.c, u0.c0, f4."Id", f4."Id0", f6."Id", f6."Id0"
FROM (
    SELECT u."Id", u."FirstName", u."LastName", u."UserName", (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f
        WHERE u."Id" = f."FollowingId") AS c, (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f0
        WHERE u."Id" = f0."FollowerId") AS c0
    FROM "Users" AS u
    WHERE NOT (u."IsDeleted") AND u."Id" = @__userId_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS u0
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f3."Id", f3."Id0", f3."FollowingId"
    FROM (
        SELECT f1."FollowerId" AS "Id", f1."Id" AS "Id0", f1."FollowingId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f1."FollowingId" ORDER BY f1."Id" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Follows" AS f1
    ) AS f3
    WHERE f3.row <= 10
) AS f4 ON u0."Id" = f4."FollowingId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f5."Id", f5."Id0", f5."FollowerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT f2."FollowingId" AS "Id", f2."Id" AS "Id0", f2."FollowerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f2."FollowerId" ORDER BY f2."Id" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Follows" AS f2
    ) AS f5
    WHERE f5.row <= 10
) AS f6 ON u0."Id" = f6."FollowerId"
ORDER BY u0."Id", f4."FollowingId", f4."Id0" DESC, f6."FollowerId", f6."Id0" DESC

) AS p0

SELECT u0."Id", u0."FirstName", u0."LastName", u0."UserName", u0.c, u0.c0, f4."Id", f4."Id0", f6."Id", f6."Id0"
FROM (
    SELECT u."Id", u."FirstName", u."LastName", u."UserName", (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f
        WHERE u."Id" = f."FollowingId") AS c, (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f0
        WHERE u."Id" = f0."FollowerId") AS c0
    FROM "Users" AS u
    WHERE NOT (u."IsDeleted") AND u."UserName" = @__userName_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS u0
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f3."Id", f3."Id0", f3."FollowingId"
    FROM (
        SELECT f1."FollowerId" AS "Id", f1."Id" AS "Id0", f1."FollowingId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f1."FollowingId" ORDER BY f1."Id" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Follows" AS f1
    ) AS f3
    WHERE f3.row <= 10
) AS f4 ON u0."Id" = f4."FollowingId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f5."Id", f5."Id0", f5."FollowerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT f2."FollowingId" AS "Id", f2."Id" AS "Id0", f2."FollowerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f2."FollowerId" ORDER BY f2."Id" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Follows" AS f2
    ) AS f5
    WHERE f5.row <= 10
) AS f6 ON u0."Id" = f6."FollowerId"
ORDER BY u0."Id", f4."FollowingId", f4."Id0" DESC, f6."FollowerId", f6."Id0" DESC

        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f0
        WHERE u."Id" = f0."FollowerId") AS c0
    FROM "Users" AS u
    WHERE NOT (u."IsDeleted") AND u."Id" = @__userId_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS u0
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f3."Id", f3."Id0", f3."FollowingId"
    FROM (
        SELECT f1."FollowerId" AS "Id", f1."Id" AS "Id0", f1."FollowingId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f1."FollowingId" ORDER BY f1."Id" DESC) AS row

    ) AS f3
    WHERE f3.row <= 10

    SELECT f5."Id", f5."Id0", f5."FollowerId"

        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f
        WHERE u."Id" = f."FollowingId") AS c, (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f0
        WHERE u."Id" = f0."FollowerId") AS c0
    FROM "Users" AS u
    WHERE NOT (u."IsDeleted") AND u."Id" = @__userId_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS u0
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f3."Id", f3."Id0", f3."FollowingId"
    FROM (
        SELECT f1."FollowerId" AS "Id", f1."Id" AS "Id0", f1."FollowingId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f1."FollowingId" ORDER BY f1."Id" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Follows" AS f1
    ) AS f3
    WHERE f3.row <= 10
) AS f4 ON u0."Id" = f4."FollowingId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f5."Id", f5."Id0", f5."FollowerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT f2."FollowingId" AS "Id", f2."Id" AS "Id0", f2."FollowerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f2."FollowerId" ORDER BY f2."Id" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Follows" AS f2
    ) AS f5
    WHERE f5.row <= 10
) AS f6 ON u0."Id" = f6."FollowerId"

FROM (
    SELECT u."Id", u."FirstName", u."LastName", u."UserName", (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f
        WHERE u."Id" = f."FollowingId") AS c, (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f0
        WHERE u."Id" = f0."FollowerId") AS c0
    FROM "Users" AS u
    WHERE NOT (u."IsDeleted") AND u."UserName" = @__userName_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS u0

    SELECT f3."Id", f3."Id0", f3."FollowingId"

        SELECT f1."FollowerId" AS "Id", f1."Id" AS "Id0", f1."FollowingId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f1."FollowingId" ORDER BY f1."Id" DESC) AS row

    WHERE f3.row <= 10
) AS f4 ON u0."Id" = f4."FollowingId"

) AS f6 ON u0."Id" = f6."FollowerId"

SELECT u0."Id", u0."FirstName", u0."LastName", u0."UserName", u0.c, u0.c0, f4."Id", f4."Id0", f6."Id", f6."Id0"
FROM (
    SELECT u."Id", u."FirstName", u."LastName", u."UserName", (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f
        WHERE u."Id" = f."FollowingId") AS c, (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f0
        WHERE u."Id" = f0."FollowerId") AS c0
    FROM "Users" AS u
    WHERE NOT (u."IsDeleted") AND u."Id" = @__userId_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS u0
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f3."Id", f3."Id0", f3."FollowingId"
    FROM (
        SELECT f1."FollowerId" AS "Id", f1."Id" AS "Id0", f1."FollowingId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f1."FollowingId" ORDER BY f1."Id" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Follows" AS f1
    ) AS f3
    WHERE f3.row <= 10
) AS f4 ON u0."Id" = f4."FollowingId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f5."Id", f5."Id0", f5."FollowerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT f2."FollowingId" AS "Id", f2."Id" AS "Id0", f2."FollowerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f2."FollowerId" ORDER BY f2."Id" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Follows" AS f2
    ) AS f5
    WHERE f5.row <= 10
) AS f6 ON u0."Id" = f6."FollowerId"
ORDER BY u0."Id", f4."FollowingId", f4."Id0" DESC, f6."FollowerId", f6."Id0" DESC

SELECT u0."Id", u0."FirstName", u0."LastName", u0."UserName", u0.c, u0.c0, f4."Id", f4."Id0", f6."Id", f6."Id0"
FROM (
    SELECT u."Id", u."FirstName", u."LastName", u."UserName", (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f
        WHERE u."Id" = f."FollowingId") AS c, (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f0
        WHERE u."Id" = f0."FollowerId") AS c0
    FROM "Users" AS u
    WHERE NOT (u."IsDeleted") AND u."UserName" = @__userName_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS u0
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f3."Id", f3."Id0", f3."FollowingId"
    FROM (
        SELECT f1."FollowerId" AS "Id", f1."Id" AS "Id0", f1."FollowingId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f1."FollowingId" ORDER BY f1."Id" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Follows" AS f1
    ) AS f3
    WHERE f3.row <= 10
) AS f4 ON u0."Id" = f4."FollowingId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f5."Id", f5."Id0", f5."FollowerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT f2."FollowingId" AS "Id", f2."Id" AS "Id0", f2."FollowerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f2."FollowerId" ORDER BY f2."Id" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Follows" AS f2
    ) AS f5
    WHERE f5.row <= 10
) AS f6 ON u0."Id" = f6."FollowerId"
ORDER BY u0."Id", f4."FollowingId", f4."Id0" DESC, f6."FollowerId", f6."Id0" DESC

SELECT u0."Id", u0."FirstName", u0."LastName", u0."UserName", u0.c, u0.c0, f4."Id", f4."Id0", f6."Id", f6."Id0"
FROM (
    SELECT u."Id", u."FirstName", u."LastName", u."UserName", (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f
        WHERE u."Id" = f."FollowingId") AS c, (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f0
        WHERE u."Id" = f0."FollowerId") AS c0
    FROM "Users" AS u
    WHERE NOT (u."IsDeleted") AND u."Id" = @__userId_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS u0
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f3."Id", f3."Id0", f3."FollowingId"
    FROM (
        SELECT f1."FollowerId" AS "Id", f1."Id" AS "Id0", f1."FollowingId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f1."FollowingId" ORDER BY f1."Id" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Follows" AS f1
    ) AS f3
    WHERE f3.row <= 10
) AS f4 ON u0."Id" = f4."FollowingId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f5."Id", f5."Id0", f5."FollowerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT f2."FollowingId" AS "Id", f2."Id" AS "Id0", f2."FollowerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f2."FollowerId" ORDER BY f2."Id" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Follows" AS f2
    ) AS f5
    WHERE f5.row <= 10
) AS f6 ON u0."Id" = f6."FollowerId"
ORDER BY u0."Id", f4."FollowingId", f4."Id0" DESC, f6."FollowerId", f6."Id0" DESC

FROM (
    SELECT u."Id", u."FirstName", u."LastName", u."UserName", (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f
        WHERE u."Id" = f."FollowingId") AS c, (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f0
        WHERE u."Id" = f0."FollowerId") AS c0
    FROM "Users" AS u
    WHERE NOT (u."IsDeleted") AND u."Id" = @__userId_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS u0
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f3."Id", f3."Id0", f3."FollowingId"
    FROM (
        SELECT f1."FollowerId" AS "Id", f1."Id" AS "Id0", f1."FollowingId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f1."FollowingId" ORDER BY f1."Id" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Follows" AS f1
    ) AS f3
    WHERE f3.row <= 10
) AS f4 ON u0."Id" = f4."FollowingId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f5."Id", f5."Id0", f5."FollowerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT f2."FollowingId" AS "Id", f2."Id" AS "Id0", f2."FollowerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f2."FollowerId" ORDER BY f2."Id" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Follows" AS f2
    ) AS f5
    WHERE f5.row <= 10
) AS f6 ON u0."Id" = f6."FollowerId"

FROM (
    SELECT u."Id", u."FirstName", u."LastName", u."UserName", (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f
        WHERE u."Id" = f."FollowingId") AS c, (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f0
        WHERE u."Id" = f0."FollowerId") AS c0
    FROM "Users" AS u
    WHERE NOT (u."IsDeleted") AND u."Id" = @__userId_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS u0
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f3."Id", f3."Id0", f3."FollowingId"
    FROM (
        SELECT f1."FollowerId" AS "Id", f1."Id" AS "Id0", f1."FollowingId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f1."FollowingId" ORDER BY f1."Id" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Follows" AS f1
    ) AS f3
    WHERE f3.row <= 10
) AS f4 ON u0."Id" = f4."FollowingId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f5."Id", f5."Id0", f5."FollowerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT f2."FollowingId" AS "Id", f2."Id" AS "Id0", f2."FollowerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f2."FollowerId" ORDER BY f2."Id" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Follows" AS f2
    ) AS f5
    WHERE f5.row <= 10
) AS f6 ON u0."Id" = f6."FollowerId"
ORDER BY u0."Id", f4."FollowingId", f4."Id0" DESC, f6."FollowerId", f6."Id0" DESC

        SELECT f."FollowingId"
        FROM "Follows" AS f
        WHERE NOT (f."IsDeleted") AND f."FollowerId" = @__userId_0
    )
    ORDER BY p."CreatedAt" DESC, p."Id" DESC
    LIMIT @__p_2 OFFSET @__p_1
) AS p0
INNER JOIN "Users" AS u ON p0."UserId" = u."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Likes" AS l ON p0."Id" = l."PostId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT c."Id", c."Body", c."CreatedAt", c."DeletedAt", c."IsDeleted", c."PostId", c."UpdatedAt", c."UserId", r."CommentId", CASE

    LEFT JOIN "Responses" AS r ON c."Id" = r."Id"
) AS s ON p0."Id" = s."PostId"
